{"tid":1651443,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"記唔記得以前課室會無啦啦靜曬？","createTime":"2019-10-13T10:48:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T00:06:11.000Z","uid":111156,"like":59,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"05b8c02d9c7e13cf904681976879841fe341cd92","tid":1651443,"uid":111156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T10:48:05.000Z","msg":"中學戈陣 老師未黎之前通常課室都好嘈<br />\n有時會突然全部人都好似靜左落黎<br />\n大家就以為老師黎咗<br />\n其實就咩事都無<br />\n<br />\n其實只係一個機率嘅問題<br />\n怡好大家都係戈個moment無講野<br />\n造就左一個錯覺<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">宜家個運動都係咁</span><br />\n幾勇武都好 有時都會搵一兩日唔出休息<br />\n恰好今日 大家都無共識下休息咗<br />\n所以！大家唔好再憶測太多<br />\n<br />\n我地需要嘅係一次機會去證明大家都仲喺到！<br />\n最有可能嘅係民陣做野<br />\n希望大家唔好泄氣！"},{"pid":"a5bd6f38367d1aa63f3d2a88362510ab2676d708","tid":1651443,"uid":209543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T10:48:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"85006cfd89d7febdc91bf0f3a8a96ef1ba373044","tid":1651443,"uid":14566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T10:50:47.000Z","msg":"要其他人出黎/做野先參與既 根本係港豬<br />\n就算全香港既人against 你，都要做應該做既野<br />\n<br />\n會care 人數多少既 都係羊群"},{"pid":"426e6865d24aeed135406cec2de3e84b66b6ce1b","tid":1651443,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T10:51:41.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"a2ad285e0f9f926e6ebf0f0c09e0b844a303ae4f","tid":1651443,"uid":137616,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T10:53:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你個比喻有畫面<br />\n推下"},{"pid":"a80df60094a03a84628213d6922a97ed6320119b","tid":1651443,"uid":24984,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T10:57:43.000Z","msg":"希望係，推<br />\n唔想再見到分化撚"},{"pid":"b78c534f4f1f029cee1f8d30f7bf2cdf7763aa79","tid":1651443,"uid":205469,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid"